metadata.name: Apefellaz #1
metadata.description: A collection of 8,888 colorful undead Apefellaz looking for a new home. Each Apefellaz is jammed packed with exclusive utility, alpha and perks such as our future Metaverse development. Apefellaz is made with love by proud Deadfellaz holders. It is not affiliated with any other projects and we are continually inspired by the works of these amazing collections. All about spreading happiness, positivity, and good vibes.. come join the family!
